Achievements.Name: Endurance Racer
Achievements.Description: Do 20 consecutive time trial laps. Simple as that. Just get into the flow and keep racing.

Achievements.Name: Like the Pros
Achievements.Description: Show that you are one of the pros by beating the pro time trial difficulty level on all tracks.

Achievements.Name: Crash Course
Achievements.Description: Not crashing only means that you are not pushing it hard enough.

Achievements.Name: Perfectionist
Achievements.Description: You wanna be fast, but still you don't wanna scratch that new space ship of yours.

Achievements.Name: Racing with Friends
Achievements.Description: Take your local friends and family on a trip into the hyper-future.

Achievements.Name: Do it With Style
Achievements.Description: Spin and jump through the level while still maintaining a fast racing line.

Achievements.Name: Its full of stars
Achievements.Description: Why only collect a few stars if you can collect them all? Go out there and find them all.

Achievements.Name: The Sky is the Limit
Achievements.Description: Where are your limits, and where are the limits of your world?

Achievements.Name: Space Tourist
Achievements.Description: You haven't seen the game until you've seen all the tracks. Still, there might be more to it.

Achievements.Name: Circus Artist
Achievements.Description: Try using the turbo rings to add a little extra speed to your tricks and spins.

Achievements.Name: Experienced Flyer
Achievements.Description: Collect enough XP to unlock the second track in the game.

Achievements.Name: Space Ship Zen
Achievements.Description: Relax, take it easy. Slow down for a while and enjoy the game in super slo-mo.

Achievements.Name: Faster, Faster, Faster!
Achievements.Description: Try turning the game's speed up to eleven. Do a fast lap in time trial to really test your skills.
